{"parse":{"title":"Raw Slitherskin Mackerel","pageid":37916,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|sell={{cost|c=1}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_24\n|quality=Common\n|itemid=6303\n|charges=1\n|stack=20\n|ilvl=5\n|name=Raw Slitherskin Mackerel\n|level=1\n|effect=Use: Restores 30 health over 15 sec.  Must remain seated while eating.}}</onlyinclude>\n\n== Source ==\nThis item can be looted from most level 6-12 [[Humanoid]] mobs.\n\n== Ingredient for ==\n\n;Cooking\nThis item is used to make: \n* {{loot|Common|Slitherskin Mackerel}}\n\n== External links ==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|6303}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/raw_slitherskin_mackerel.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft food items]]\n[[Category:Fish]]"}}}